# ===================================================================
# Yarn Berry (Plug'n'Play with Zero-Installs)
#
# DO commit:
#   - .yarn/cache            (The package archives)
#   - .yarn/releases         (The Yarn binary itself)
#   - .yarn/plugins          (Any plugins you add)
#   - .pnp.cjs               (The Plug'n'Play resolution file)
#   - .yarnrc.yml            (Yarn's configuration file)
#
# DO NOT commit:
#   - .yarn/unplugged        (Packages that need to be extracted)
#   - .yarn/build-state.yml  (Build-related cache)
#   - .yarn/install-state.gz (Installation metadata)
# ===================================================================
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.gz

# Exclude the Yarn cache to avoid large file issues with GitHub
.yarn/cache
